{"lemma": "عَثْرَةٌ", "slug": "عَثْرَةٌ", "root": "ع.ث.ر", "root_slug": "ع-ث-ر", "root_link": "/words/roots/ع-ث-ر", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": false}, "wiktextract": {"found": false}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n28032"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%AB%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "stumble, slip, fault", "fa": "لغزش، اشتباه", "ur": "پھسلنا، غلطی", "tr": "düşme, hata", "id": "jatuh, kesalahan", "bn": "পা পিছলানো, ভুল", "es": "tropiezo, falta", "fr": "chute, faute", "de": "Stolpern, Fehler", "ru": "спотыкание, ошибка", "zh": "绊倒，过失"}, "definition": null, "etymology": null, "ipa": null, "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n28032", "headword_ar": "عَثْرَةٌ", "root": "Evr", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A stumble,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "trip,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in walking,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "going along:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EavaraAtN", "text_ar": "عَثَرَاتٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) ―         -b2-  And [hence,] (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A slip, lapse, fault, wrong action,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mistake;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, Msb, TA;) so called as being"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a fall into sin"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "crime."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) One says,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aqaAla A@ll~`hu Eavorataka", "text_ar": "اَقَالَ ا@للّٰهُ عَثْرَتَكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "May God cancel thy slip, lapse, fault,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.]. (A.) And it is said in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laA Haliyma A_il~aA *uw EavorapK", "text_ar": "لَا حَلِيمَ اـِلَّا ذُو عَثْرَةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e. (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "There is no one"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "to be characterized as"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of a forbearing disposition except"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "he be"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "one who has committed a slip,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and becomes admonished thereby, distinguishing the occasions of error so as to avoid them [and to make allowance for others who have done the like]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "War,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fight, against unbelievers"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "others;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "because war, or fight, is an occasion of frequent stumbling, or tripping: so in a trad., in which it is said,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laA tabodaA^ohumo biAlEavorapi", "text_ar": "لَا تَبْدَاْهُمْ بِالعَثْرَةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Begin not ye with them by war"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; meaning invite ye them first to El-Islám or to the payment of the poll-tax; and if they assent not, then have recourse to war. (TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["Msb", "TA"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}